==English==
===Pronunciation===
*/kɒmikɒze/ (IPA) - This is the standard pronunciation of the word.
*/ˌkæməˈkaːziː/ - Many Americans mispronounce the word this way.

===Etymology===
From Japanese [[神風]] (かみかぜ, kamikaze), ''divine wind''.

===Noun===
'''kamikaze'''

#an [[attack]] requiring the [[suicide]] of the one carrying it out, especially when done with an aircraft.
#one who makes such an attack

